OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMainly fine although again on
OL,6,Fthe cloudy side, especially over east-
OL,7,Ffacing higher ground and some coastal
OL,8,Fdistricts. A little further rain is
OL,9,Fpossible, perhaps showery later. Warm
OL,10,Fand humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,13,FIncreasingly fine after some cloudy
OL,14,Fstarts, and becoming widely very warm,
OL,15,Fwith warm intervening nights. Chance
OL,16,Fof some thundery showers developing
OL,17,Flater Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
